-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>故事发生于两万年前的欧洲北部，地球正处于弱肉强食的冰川时期心地善良的男主角科达是部落首领的儿子，在一次部落集体狩猎中，科达不慎跌落悬崖，众人以为科达已死，但大难不死的科达被洪水卷走幸存下来，只身流落荒野。途中科达与一匹野狼相遇，给它起名阿尔法，意即狼群首领。科达在与其相处的过程中逐渐成长，学习“狼性</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/35366/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/46257/" data-original="http://pic.iqiyi6123.com/upload/vod/2019-01-17/15477286099.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">4.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">BD高清</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/46257/">阿尔法与欧米加2</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E6%9C%AC%C2%B7%E8%BF%AA%E6%96%AF%E9%87%91------------/" target="_blank">本·迪斯金</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Kate------------/" target="_blank">Kate</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Higgins------------/" target="_blank">Higgins</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Lindsay------------/" target="_blank">Lindsay</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Torrance------------/" target="_blank">Torrance</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-Liza------------/" target="_blank">Liza</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-West------------/" target="_blank">West</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----Richard--------/" target="_blank">Richard</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-----Rich--------/" target="_blank">Rich</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/22/" target="_blank">其他片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD-----------/" target="_blank">美国</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2013/" target="_blank">2013</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>凯特（Kate）和 亨弗雷（Humphrey）还有他们的3个孩子 (Stinky, Claudette and Runt) 正在兴致勃勃地准备一起庆祝他们的第一个冬天，而他们最小的幼崽Runt，却神秘地消失了此刻，他们必须跨越旷野前往新的征程，在大雪封路之前找到并带回 Runt。这是他们的最大的冒险</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/46257/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/45090/" data-original="http://pic.iqiyi6123.com/upload/vod/2019-01-17/15477279669.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">1.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">BD高清</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/45090/">阿尔法城</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%9F%83%E8%BF%AA%C2%B7%E5%BA%B7%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%E4%B8%81------------/" target="_blank">埃迪·康斯坦丁</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%AE%89%E5%A8%9C%C2%B7%E5%8D%A1%E9%87%8C%E5%A8%9C------------/" target="_blank">安娜·卡里娜</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%98%BF%E5%9F%BA%E5%A7%86%C2%B7%E5%9D%A6%E7%B1%B3%E7%BD%97%E5%A4%AB------------/" target="_blank">阿基姆·坦米罗夫</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%AE%A9-%E7%9A%AE%E5%9F%83%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E5%88%A9%E5%A5%A5%E5%BE%B7------------/" target="_blank">让-皮埃尔·利奥德</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E8%AE%A9-%E5%90%95%E5%85%8B%C2%B7%E6%88%88%E8%BE%BE%E5%B0%94--------/" target="_blank">让-吕克·戈达尔</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/11/" target="_blank">剧情片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E6%B3%95%E5%9B%BD-----------/" target="_blank">法国</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------1965/" target="_blank">1965</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>这是一座死寂冰冷的未来都市，一座无爱无情的“死城”一切都必须遵循一台名为“阿尔法60”超级计算机统治下的“逻辑”，若有违反者，都会被枪决。生活在这里的人们表情木讷，生活思维受到严格的控制，丧失了一切人性本该拥有的喜怒哀乐。来自另外世界的密探雷米·柯雄（埃迪·康斯坦丁 Eddie Constantin</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/45090/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/40612/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2018-11-23/201811231542945293.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">6.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/40612/">阿尔法：狼伴归途</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E6%9F%AF%E8%92%82%C2%B7%E6%96%AF%E5%AF%86%E7%89%B9-%E9%BA%A6%E8%8F%B2%E5%A8%9C%E5%A1%94%E8%8E%8E%C2%B7%E8%BF%88%E5%B0%94%E5%85%B9------------/" target="_blank">柯蒂·斯密特-麦菲娜塔莎·迈尔兹</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E8%89%BE%E5%B0%94%E4%BC%AF%E7%89%B9%C2%B7%E4%BC%91%E6%96%AF--------/" target="_blank">艾尔伯特·休斯</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-------------/" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/11/" target="_blank">剧情片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD-----------/" target="_blank">美国</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>故事发生于两万年前的欧洲北部，地球正处于弱肉强食的冰川时期心地善良的男主角科达是部落首领的儿子，在一次部落集体狩猎中，科达不慎跌落悬崖，众人以为科达已死，但大难不死的科达被洪水卷走幸存下来，只身流落荒野。 　　途中科达与一匹野狼相遇，给它起名阿尔法，意即狼群首领。科达在与其相处的过程中逐渐成长，学习</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/40612/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><div class="fed-page-info fed-text-center"><a class="fed-btns-info fed-rims-info fed-hide fed-show-xs-inline fed-btns-disad" href="/s/%E9%98%BF%E5%B0%94%E6%B3%95------------/">首页</a><a class="fed-btns-info fed-rims-info fed-btns-disad" href="/s/%E9%98%BF%E5%B